posts.name: Will Toth
posts.cooked:
Tableau has been so weird with their FIRST licence donations, and it makes no sense at all. I’m fairly sure its been directly asked of them to make it a 1 year license too.

It further makes no sense since they already offer 1 year free student licenses https://www.tableau.com/academic/students which can be a workaround for teams.

This has been a yearly struggle. Tableau is fantastic, but he licensing has us evaluating other optons.

posts.name: MikLast
posts.cooked:
vmorgs:

What is this FRC Team Advocate of which you speak?

frcteamadvocate@firstinspires.org is the contact, they are meant to advocate for the teams to FIRST about issues you have, big and small.

You can learn more about the role here , though Jamee left the role in late 2020.
